{"id":894,"parent_id":890,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":894,"title":"Hosea 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hosea","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Israel loses all truth, mercy, and knowledge of God and goes whoring after false gods."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.1","order":"02.29.004.60158"},["b","1"],"Hear the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", ye children of Israel: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"controversy"],"with the inhabitants of the land, because",["i","there is"],"no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"truth"],", nor mercy, nor",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"knowledge"],"of God in the land."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.2","order":"02.29.004.60159"},["b","2"],"By",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"swearing"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"lying"],", and killing, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"stealing"],", and committing adultery, they",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"break out"],", and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"blood toucheth blood"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.3","order":"02.29.004.60160"},["b","3"],"Therefore shall the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"land"],"mourn, and every one that dwelleth therein shall languish, with the beasts of the field, and with the fowls of heaven; yea, the fishes of the sea also shall be taken away."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.4","order":"02.29.004.60161"},["b","4"],"Yet let no man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"strive"],", nor reprove another: for thy people",["i","are"],"as they that strive with the priest."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.5","order":"02.29.004.60162"},["b","5"],"Therefore shalt thou fall in the day, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"prophet"],"also shall fall with thee in the night, and I will destroy thy mother."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.6","order":"02.29.004.60163"},["b","6"],"¶My people are destroyed for lack of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"knowledge"],": because thou hast",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"rejected"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"knowledge"],", I will also reject thee, that thou shalt be no priest to me: seeing thou hast forgotten the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"law"],"of thy God, I will also forget thy children."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.7","order":"02.29.004.60164"},["b","7"],"As they were increased, so they sinned against me:",["i","therefore"],"will I change their glory into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.8","order":"02.29.004.60165"},["b","8"],"They eat up the sin of my people, and they set their heart on their iniquity."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.9","order":"02.29.004.60166"},["b","9"],"And there shall be, like people, like priest: and I will punish them for their ways, and reward them their doings."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.10","order":"02.29.004.60167"},["b","10"],"For they shall eat, and not have enough: they shall commit whoredom, and shall not increase: because they have left off to take heed to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.11","order":"02.29.004.60168"},["b","11"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Whoredom"],"and wine and new wine take away the heart."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.12","order":"02.29.004.60169"},["b","12"],"¶My people ask",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"counsel"],"at their stocks, and their staff declareth unto them: for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"spirit"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"whoredoms"],"hath caused",["i","them"],"to err, and they have gone a whoring from under their God."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.13","order":"02.29.004.60170"},["b","13"],"They sacrifice upon the tops of the mountains, and burn incense upon the hills, under oaks and poplars and elms, because the shadow thereof",["i","is"],"good: therefore your daughters shall commit whoredom, and your spouses shall commit",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"adultery"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.14","order":"02.29.004.60171"},["b","14"],"I will not punish your daughters when they commit whoredom, nor your spouses when they commit adultery: for themselves are separated with whores, and they sacrifice with harlots: therefore the people",["i","that"],"doth not understand shall fall."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.15","order":"02.29.004.60172"},["b","15"],"¶Though thou, Israel, play the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"harlot"],",",["i","yet"],"let not Judah offend; and come not ye unto Gilgal, neither go ye up to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"Beth-aven"],", nor swear, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"liveth."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.16","order":"02.29.004.60173"},["b","16"],"For Israel slideth back as a backsliding heifer: now the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will feed them as a lamb in a large place."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.17","order":"02.29.004.60174"},["b","17"],"Ephraim",["i","is"],"joined to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"idols"],": let him alone."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.18","order":"02.29.004.60175"},["b","18"],"Their drink is sour: they have committed whoredom continually: her rulers",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},["i","with"],"shame do love"],", Give ye."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.19","order":"02.29.004.60176"},["b","19"],"The wind hath bound her up in her wings, and they shall be ashamed because of their sacrifices."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.1a","order":"02.29.004.60177"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.31"},"Jer. 25:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/12.2.1-2"},"Hosea 12:2 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/6.2"},"Micah 6:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.1b","order":"02.29.004.60179"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/truth"},"TG Truth"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.1c","order":"02.29.004.60181"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.2a","order":"02.29.004.60183"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/profanity"},"TG Profanity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/swearing"},"Swearing"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.2b","order":"02.29.004.60185"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"TG Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.2c","order":"02.29.004.60187"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stealing"},"TG Stealing"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.2d","order":"02.29.004.60189"},["b","2d"],["span.small","IE"],"break all bounds."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.2e","order":"02.29.004.60191"},["b","2e"],["span.small","OR"],"bloodshed leads to bloodshed."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.3a","order":"02.29.004.60193"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.10"},"Joel 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.4a","order":"02.29.004.60195"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/contention"},"TG Contention"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.5a","order":"02.29.004.60197"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.6a","order":"02.29.004.60199"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ignorance"},"Ignorance"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.6b","order":"02.29.004.60201"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.6c","order":"02.29.004.60203"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"TG Knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.6d","order":"02.29.004.60205"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.7a","order":"02.29.004.60207"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.11a","order":"02.29.004.60209"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/whore"},"TG Whore"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.12a","order":"02.29.004.60211"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"TG Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.12b","order":"02.29.004.60213"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.20"},"Isa. 44:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/1.21"},"Rom. 1:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.12c","order":"02.29.004.60215"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/whore"},"TG Whore"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.13a","order":"02.29.004.60217"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.15a","order":"02.29.004.60219"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.15.15,34"},"Ezek. 16:15 (15, 34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.15b","order":"02.29.004.60221"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.8.7-8"},"Hosea 10:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.17a","order":"02.29.004.60223"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.18a","order":"02.29.004.60225"},["b","18a"],["span.small","OR"],"deeply love dishonor."]]}
